caption:
Don’t necessarily think of Nunavut when it comes to fall colours? Let this stunning photo from Sirmilik National Park change your mind! Prime visiting time is May to September, so you’ve got lots of time to start planning your adventure to one of Nunavut’s most accessible parks!
